## DM Notes — Round 1

**Oryn's turn:** Players likely open with area control — Fog Cloud or Grease useless here (water). Expect Fireball or Hold Person.

**Warden A:** Multiattack, moves to engage nearest PC. Bonus: **Funerary Brand** — on hit, target makes DC 14 Con save or loses reaction until start of next turn.

**Revenant turn:** Rises dramatically from the water. Describe: *"The water erupts. Something that was once a man stands, jaw unhinged, barnacles fused into its ribcage."* Uses **Corrupting Gaze** — one PC DC 15 Wis save or frightened until end of *Revenant's* next turn.

> **Foreshadowing:** The water near the far altar has started spiraling. Nobody knows why yet. [[z=4|reveal in Round 3]]

