## DM Notes — Round 2

**Revenant Regen:** Add 10 HP back at start of its turn — UNLESS it took radiant or fire damage last round. Mark accordingly.

**Warden Synergy (if both alive):** Wardens use **Tomb Bond** — if within 10 ft of each other, they have advantage on attack rolls. Reward players who split them up.

**Thaddeus:** Spiritual Weapon should be live by now. The cleric's player will want to know the Revenant's weakness — DC 15 Religion check reveals: *"Revenants are bound to an unfulfilled obsession. Destroying the object of that obsession ends regeneration permanently."*

**The Obsession Object:** A sealed iron coffer on the altar at the far end (AC 15, 22 HP). Wardens will move to protect it if threatened.

> **Escalation:** Water level rises 6 inches at end of this round. Announce it ominously. No mechanical effect yet. [[z=3|effect kicks in Round 3]]

